<div class="details theme-blue" data-id="7114311" data-title="Fernie residents discover surprising family history during Juno Beach visit" data-tag="363780" data-momentum="off">
<h1 class="title details-title">Fernie residents discover surprising family history during Juno Beach visit</h1>
    <div class="details-intro">The Yuills found their family’s Second World War history while on a European sailing trip</div>

        <div class="byline-area">
