                <div class="galleryCaption">
                        <span id="galleryStats"><span id="galleryStatsCurrent">1</span> / <span id="galleryStatsOf">1</span></span>
                    <span id="galleryCaption">Deryk Yuill stands beside his uncle Ronald Brewer’s grave in Graye-sur-Mer Cemetery in France. He and his family uncovered the history behind his uncle’s wartime service at Juno Beach while on a sailing trip off the coast of Northwest Europe (Photo courtesy of Yuill family) </span><span id="galleryByline"></span>
                    <span id="galleryAdCaption" class="hidden">Advertisement</span>
